subproject.description: The project aims to provide alternate housing to 100 families in the north of Gaza Strip in addition to one school, one mosque and physical infrastructure (roads, water and waste water networks and electricity networks). The project will also generate of around 50,000 workdays to alleviate poverty.  And detailed design of the re housing units and related infrastructure will be undertaken.
